<!channel>: Happy Monday Everyone! As Stephanie mentioned on Friday, we're holding our Open House tonight from 5-7 in the Social Space. Since our incredible office manager is out this week, I would appreciate any help I can get from all of you beautiful people.  A few things I could use a little help with: 
1.) Signs to direct people to the space. 
2.) General pre-party cleanup including relocation of expensive items and proprietary information (We will make sure to keep everyone in the 390 space - so if you must work during the event, we’ll make sure not to bug you)
3.) Someone to make an Olympic Provisions run between 2:20 and 3pm (Platters should be ready for pickup at 2:30, and they close at 3pm today. I have a few meetings that prevent me from picking it up, so if someone can grab my card and swing by - it would be SUPER helpful)
4.) Sound System setup ( <@U026PHQ3J> ?)
5.) Slide show setup ( christmas party slides perhaps?)
6.) Your presence!!! A bunch of people have RSVP’d and want to know about what we’re up to. Here’s your chance to show off :simple_smile:

Thank you all so much! Let’s celebrate all of the amazing things UCS has accomplished since moving out of PIE :simple_smile:
